{"tid":1944882,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"強制隔離第三日，我出咗街","createTime":"2020-03-26T16:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T15:07:38.000Z","uid":133377,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"619b93ca6b5606329060809135dd7db53b25837e","tid":1944882,"uid":133377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T16:36:49.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我早幾日喺外國翻嚟，戴咗手帶翻屋企隔離。尋日有兩個密切接觸過既朋友中咗，入咗醫院。我本身冇驗過，又懷疑自己可能中咗（輕微病徵），所以穩陣起見打咗去衛生署。夜晚佢地覆翻安排到深喉測試，但係要由我屋企（港島）去北大嶼山醫院驗，用救護車接。<br />\n<br />\n咁我問衛生署熱線條友，如果我離開咗我個隔離單位有冇問題啦，佢話衛生署同資訊科技嗰邊係冇關係，叫我自己同佢地講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家我已經離開咗單位超過四個鐘都未有人打俾我，淨係個app叫過我影相確認位置，所以即係話條帶其實係廢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行均港九新界都冇人捉我，影住自己喺大嶼山都冇人理<br />\n<br />\n都費事提條帶鬆到會跌出嚟，有人一個星期都收唔到sms呢啲on9嘢，原來戴住條帶出去成晚政府都唔會理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有嘢想問隨便問（驗既過程/點打去問），等緊測試結果，要坐多6-8個鐘頭"},{"pid":"cd9d05b8cfcd5195fd047b1b6b108a163cec9046","tid":1944882,"uid":183322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T16:39:36.000Z","msg":"有冇去報失"},{"pid":"f4d1ee5b27e1c2b7bcc8e183f18b1f8dcbbd3e73","tid":1944882,"uid":133377,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T16:43:15.000Z","msg":"送咗兩包餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痴線，喺個咁高風險既環境除罩食嘢係咩玩法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d59b30cd4e8a20a83623047f125f4f854565bc","tid":1944882,"uid":161770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T16:53:52.000Z","msg":"無得過嚟探樓豬了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b158b5d6f54dd94f43bcdb4f1d86424d41e61ae","tid":1944882,"uid":80902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T16:55:10.000Z","msg":"政府on99"},{"pid":"37262b2f621e6cf92818438cb132d29bf0d09720","tid":1944882,"uid":106027,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T16:56:44.000Z","msg":"壞咗要去警署整"},{"pid":"6e577488547859322d71c8c2f04c9b3cba49595b","tid":1944882,"uid":133377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T01:57:20.000Z","msg":"補充翻，結果係陰性，但係到而家都冇人打電話嚟問我去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10個鐘頭行勻港九新界都係冇人理"},{"pid":"47a95e867a12726dc6096803eabf91177717c80f","tid":1944882,"uid":133377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T08:12:28.000Z","msg":"衛生署終於打嚟，不過個對話鳩到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「衛生署呀，想問下你喺唔喺屋企」<br />\n「喺呀」<br />\n「好啦byebye」<br />\n<br />\n連我出咗去成晚都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb8d44d2101e2287977e5ca47ff073e6f2252971","tid":1944882,"uid":317378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47a95e867a12726dc6096803eabf91177717c80f","tid":1944882,"uid":133377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T08:12:28.000Z","msg":"衛生署終於打嚟，不過個對話鳩到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「衛生署呀，想問下你喺唔喺屋企」<br />\n「喺呀」<br />\n「好啦byebye」<br />\n<br />\n連我出咗去成晚都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T08:19:58.000Z","msg":"根本手帶呢樣野就係扮做左野，厄d無判斷力ge市民用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6eed97f36828ba65e918cc1194969378ca7d58a","tid":1944882,"uid":137085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T14:56:05.000Z","msg":"樓主最後有冇事?<br />\n我都隔離緊, 想驗既話打邊個電話?"},{"pid":"142c5b3c913ec410b17f32507ad35ecac2d39856","tid":1944882,"uid":133377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6eed97f36828ba65e918cc1194969378ca7d58a","tid":1944882,"uid":137085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T14:56:05.000Z","msg":"樓主最後有冇事?<br />\n我都隔離緊, 想驗既話打邊個電話?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T15:07:38.000Z","msg":"最後冇事，正常打衛生署